Introduction to White-throated Sparrows, color morph, and size differences.

ggplot(WTSPdata, aes(fat, morph)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth() +
  xlab ("Fat (grams)") +
  ylab ("Color Morph") +
  labs(title="Raw Fit: 1 = White morph, 0 = Tan morph")


fit.1 <- glm(morph~fat, data=WTSPdata, binomial(link="logit"))
autoplot(fit.1)
